12::[MP]::
2MP is used for casting spells.  When you cast a spell it will decrease your current MP.
12::[How do I check my MP?]::
2Syntax: 12!mp
2This command will display how much MP you have in the format of current / max
12::[How do I Get More MP?]::
2Your MP will increase when you level up. The amount you gain per level is dependent on your current job. Piety is the most important stat when it comes to MP.